OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781592466
OL,3,CEight dead in B-52 bomber crash at US
OL,4,CAir Force base in California
OL,6,FA B-52 bomber crashed shortly after
OL,7,Ftakeoff at a US Air Force base in
OL,8,FCalifornia's Mojave Desert on Monday
OL,9,Fand burst into flames, killing all
OL,10,Feight people aboard, military
OL,11,Fofficials said.
OL,13,FAerial footage showed virtually
OL,14,Fnothing left of the aircraft that went
OL,15,Fdown during a routine test mission at
OL,16,FEdwards Air Force Base, which is north
OL,17,Fof Los Angeles.
OL,19,FThose on the B-52 included government
OL,20,Fcontractors and uniformed military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
