PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781592466
OL,3,CEight dead in B-52 bomber crash at US
OL,4,CAir Force base in California
OL,6,FAircraft manufacturer Boeing confirmed
OL,7,Fon Monday evening that two of its
OL,8,Femployees were on board.
OL,10,FAfter reviewing footage of the crash,
OL,11,Fit was determined that no one could
OL,12,Fhave survived, Colonel James Hayes,
OL,13,Fthe deputy commander for the 412 test
OL,14,Fwing at Edwards, said at a news
OL,15,Fconference.
OL,17,F"We lost eight great Americans," Hayes
OL,18,Fsaid, adding that officials were
OL,19,Fworking to notify their families.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
