FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781592466
OL,3,CEight dead in B-52 bomber crash at US
OL,4,CAir Force base in California
OL,6,FIt was not immediately clear what
OL,7,Fcaused the crash, and it could take up
OL,8,Fto six months to complete an
OL,9,Finvestigation, Hayes said, but shared
OL,10,Fthat the B-52 was supporting the
OL,11,F"radar modernisation program."
OL,13,FThe Boeing B-52 Stratofortress is a
OL,14,Flong-range bomber that entered service
OL,15,Fin 1955. Designed to carry both
OL,16,Fconventional and nuclear weapons, it
OL,17,Fhas been used in conflicts involving
OL,18,Fthe US military from Vietnam to Iran.
