OL,3,CEight dead in B-52 bomber crash at US
OL,4,CAir Force base in California
OL,6,FEdwards Air Force Base is home to a
OL,7,Flarge portion of the US Air Force's
OL,8,Faircraft test and development efforts.
OL,10,FThe 412th Test Wing, which runs the
OL,11,Fbase, also conducts developmental
OL,12,Ftesting of all Air Force aircraft,
OL,13,Fweapons systems, software and
OL,14,Fcomponents before purchase by the
OL,15,Fservice as well as throughout their
OL,16,Flifespan.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
