PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781592466
OL,3,CEight dead in B-52 bomber crash at US
OL,4,CAir Force base in California
OL,6,FThe airfield was closed most of Monday
OL,7,Fand all inbound aircraft were being
OL,8,Fdiverted, but it reopened to people
OL,9,Fcoming onto the base by late afternoon.
OL,11,FNon-commercial visitor passes for the
OL,12,Fbase were suspended as emergency crews
OL,13,Fdoused the flames.
OL,15,FAir Force Secretary Troy Meink said he
OL,16,Fis deeply saddened by the lives lost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
