OL,3,CEight dead in B-52 bomber crash at US
OL,4,CAir Force base in California
OL,6,F"We mourn this loss and honor the
OL,7,Fservice of our Airmen, civilians, and
OL,8,Fcontractors who work every day to
OL,9,Fadvance our mission," he said in a
OL,10,Fpost on X.
